v0.011 UPDATE:

- complete game rewrite (wasn't happy on how it worked before)
- decreased world file size by 40 to 50 percent
- switched save file type (bytes -> json)
- switched frameworks (lwjgl -> libgdx)
- better performance
- HUGE optimization update
- lighting is introduced
- added support for linux
- added custom cursor to the game
- changed the game's icon to a grass block
- added camera lerp effect when following player
- switched texture size (32 -> 16)
- added full-screen support
- resizable window